## Secrets (never hardcode)

- `BOX_CLIENT_ID`, `BOX_CLIENT_SECRET` — Box Developer Console OAuth app
- `COOKIE_ENCRYPTION_KEY` — `openssl rand -hex 32`
- `ALLOWED_EMAIL_DOMAIN`, `ALLOWED_EMAILS` — optional access restrictions
